---
// Advertisement banner (subtle)
---

<div class="mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between border border-indigo-100 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-gray-200 text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 text-gray-500 rounded-bl-lg font-bold">PUBLICIDAD</div>
  <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4">
    <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-sm">
      <i class="ri-store-3-line text-indigo-500 text-2xl"></i>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">¿Tienes una ferretería o negocio local?</h3>
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-600">Apoya a tu comunidad y destaca aquí. <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold underline">Contáctanos</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hidden md:block">
    <i class="ri-arrow-right-line text-indigo-300 group-hover:text-indigo-500 transition text-2xl"></i>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 w-24 h-24 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
</div>
